OL,3,CMy life was "turned upside down" by
OL,4,Cdiagnosis, says man with multiple
OL,5,Csclerosis
OL,7,FA man from Co Fermanagh has told UTV
OL,8,Fhow his life was "completely turned
OL,9,Fupside down" after he was diagnosed
OL,10,Fwith multiple sclerosis (MS) aged 48.
OL,12,FRichard Barr wants to raise awareness
OL,13,Fabout the condition, which is a
OL,14,Fchronic neurological disease that
OL,15,Faffects the brain and spinal cord.
