OL,3,CMy life was "turned upside down" by
OL,4,Cdiagnosis, says man with multiple
OL,5,Csclerosis
OL,7,FHe was diagnosed in October 2024, and
OL,8,Falthough in the lead-up he had been
OL,9,Fgoing to his GP with health issues, he
OL,10,Fhad no idea what was wrong.
OL,12,FThat was until one day, he collapsed
OL,13,Fwhile working as a lorry driver.
