OL,3,CMy life was "turned upside down" by
OL,4,Cdiagnosis, says man with multiple
OL,5,Csclerosis
OL,7,FHe said: "I was in Portstewart doing a
OL,8,Fdeliveries, some collections. I was
OL,9,Ffinished doing a collection and I was
OL,10,Fclimbing up in the lorry and my legs
OL,11,Fjust gave way there. And I went down
OL,12,Flike a sack spuds. It was very scary
OL,13,Fbecause I couldn't get myself up. I
OL,14,Fwas stuck on the ground."
OL,16,FThe father from Maguiresbridge was
OL,17,Ftold he needed to see to see a
OL,18,Fneurologist but that there was a 6
OL,19,Fyear wait.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
