OL,3,CMy life was "turned upside down" by
OL,4,Cdiagnosis, says man with multiple
OL,5,Csclerosis
OL,7,FFortunately, he managed to get a CT
OL,8,Fscan at the South West Acute Hospital
OL,9,Fin Enniskillen, where he got the
OL,10,Fdiagnosis.
OL,12,FDescribing how he felt receiving the
OL,13,Fnews, he said he was "absolutely
OL,14,Fdevastated" and that he "didn't see it
OL,15,Fcoming".
