OL,3,CMy life was "turned upside down" by
OL,4,Cdiagnosis, says man with multiple
OL,5,Csclerosis
OL,7,FHe said: "I didn't know what to
OL,8,Fexpect, what was in front of me, what
OL,9,Flife would throw up. How do you I even
OL,10,Fcope? Life has completely turned
OL,11,Fupside down for me. I'm no longer able
OL,12,Fto do a job which I love to.
OL,14,F"A bad day could be me staying in bed
OL,15,For sitting here, staying down here and
OL,16,Fnot being able to move".
