OL,3,CMy life was "turned upside down" by
OL,4,Cdiagnosis, says man with multiple
OL,5,Csclerosis
OL,7,FHis wife Janet said: "Richard and I
OL,8,Fhave been married for 20 years. To to
OL,9,Fsee how active Richard was to being
OL,10,Fnot so active, especially for Hannah
OL,11,Fas well to see her daddy change so
OL,12,Fmuch, has been a big, big change for
OL,13,FHannah."
OL,15,FMr Barr added: "I'm thankful that I
OL,16,Fhave my wife, my daughter and the dog
OL,17,Fto keep me in a positive mindset.
